━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

8.1 Automatic Termination.

    Any breach of the conditions in Sections 3 or 4 immediately and
    automatically terminates all rights granted to the breaching Licensee
    under this License, without notice and without any requirement for
    action by the copyright holders.

8.2 Cure Period.

    If a Licensee becomes aware of an unintentional breach of Section 3
    (e.g., a distribution inadvertently missing the required license text),
    rights are not automatically terminated, provided the Licensee cures
    the breach within thirty (30) days of becoming aware of it.

8.3 Effect of Termination.

    Upon termination, the Licensee must immediately cease all use,
    reproduction, modification, and distribution of the Software and any
    Derivative Works. Sections 6, 7, and 9 survive termination.

